data.description: WELL MAINTAINED POOL HOME with SLAB FLOORS, BLOCK with METAL SIDING, NEW ROOF 2020, NICE YARD WITH privacy fence. THREE BEDROOMS, 1 FULL and 1 HALF BATH with OPEN FLOOR PLAN, CUSTOM CABINETS with lots of COUNTERTOP SPACE and STORAGE. Large carport with concrete driveway and landscaped front yard. Two storage sheds convey with property. Home provides the following: WATER SOFTNER FILTRATION SYSTEM with UV Light, AIR HANDLER UV LIGHT, HIGH IMPACT WINDOWS ON SOUTH SIDE OF HOME, CUSTOM CABNETS WITH UNDER CABINET LED LIGHTS with DIMMER. KITCHEN LIGHTS on DIMMER, TERRAZZO FLOORS THROUGH under tile and carpet, REVERSE OSMOSIS WATER SYSTEM IN KITCHEN, 30AMP GENERATOR PLUG BELOW THE METER which can be safely switched over at the circuit panel and supplies entire home except central AC and STOVE.   NO HOA or CDD. Close to shopping and restaurants and 7 MILES FROM THE BEACH. CENTRALLY LOCATED in WEST BRADENTON.
